'''''Classic Creatures: Return of the Jedi''''' is a [[1983]] documentary on the making of [[Star Wars: Episode VI Return of the Jedi|''Star Wars'': Episode VI ''Return of the Jedi'']]. Behind-the-scenes footage is interspersed with clips and information from classic monster movies.

Hosted and narrated by [[Billy Dee Williams]] and [[Carrie Fisher]], it was issued as a triple feature with ''[[The Making of Star Wars]]'' and ''[[SPFX: The Empire Strikes Back]]'' in 1983. It was also included in the ''[[Star Wars: The Complete Saga]]'' Blu-ray release.

